{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"69f532ccad","title":"刘少奇给宋棐卿的信","origin":"一九五七年九月，人民出版社资料室《批判资料：中国赫鲁晓夫刘少奇反革命修正主义言论集》（1958．6—1967．7）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7548841526","index":0,"year":1949,"month":5,"day":3,"articleId":"69f532ccad"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9986567b57","name":"刘少奇"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"43fa3178f2","type":"title","text":"刘少奇给宋棐卿的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"803a8d512d","type":"authors","text":"刘少奇","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"a86d2e6ae2","type":"appellation","text":"宋棐卿先生大鉴：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"a4e8ea33c8","type":"paragraph","text":"接四月三十日来函，得悉贵公司职工团结，劳资双方共同努力扩大生产，增设新厂之计划，甚为忻慰。望本公私兼顾、劳资两利之方针，继续努力，前途光明，国家民族之复兴指日可待也。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"96df5507d1","type":"paragraph","text":"顺候","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"b548c08f50","type":"appellation","text":"台安","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"272340c4b8","type":"paragraph","text":" 刘少奇五月三日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"afea36874b","type":"appellation","text":"附件：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"f25e7d7257","type":"subtitle","text":"宋棐卿给刘少奇的信(1949.04.30)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"0ce8a7744d","type":"appellation","text":"敬启者","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"adc43c7523","type":"paragraph","text":"敝厂自蒙阁下惠临训话后，全厂职工对于政府之工业政策有了新的了解及新的希望与新生命，至为愉快，因此已决定每人皆尽最大之努力以完成此伟大为人群服务之使命，而副政府及阁下关垂训示之至意。今仅将敝厂决定发展之计划奉陈如后：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"a52f153f8a","type":"paragraph","text":"1．敝麻厂决于最近期内加开夜班。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"28a878cb39","type":"paragraph","text":"2．敝毛厂决再添购原毛增加生产。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"a19f5c6719","type":"paragraph","text":"3．敝化学厂虽已停工将近一年，今已计划即行开工。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"dd8a159f39","type":"paragraph","text":"4．敝公司并正筹划再开设麻袋第二厂，以增生产。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"355d0f30dc","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各项知关","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"5d4c270612","type":"paragraph","text":"厪注，谨先将此概要奉闻，以后进行至何程度，亦必随时报告，聆受指导也。谨上","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"aa44608756","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇副主席勋鉴","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"},{"id":"fff9e443cf","type":"paragraph","text":" 宋棐卿谨启三十八年四月卅日","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad"}],"page":{"id":"2035bc4275","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f532ccad","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}